    "next_route": "One sprint: emit a WRF step-1 surface-driver hook (same disposable pattern) around module_sf_mynn/sfclayrev for TSK/ZNT/UST/HFX/QFX in/out, port the sfclayrev first-call (flag_iter/UST first-guess) semantics + skin-temperature/roughness sourcing into the JAX surface adapter, and gate on case-D converging to case-B levels; then rerun the strict Step-1 proofs against the rmol-pinned WRF truth.",
